cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR 

This paper discusses the state-of-the-art in image restoration and enhancement, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also introduces a large-scale benchmark dataset and proposes a set of metrics to evaluate algorithmic impact on visual quality and automatic object recognition, which are topics in multimedia (cs.MM), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the development of new algorithms for image restoration and enhancement, which is a topic in graphics (cs.GR).
